verbose_text: To determine the functional importance of MarvelD3 for eye development, we designed two morpholino (MO) antisense oligonucleotides that block MD3 translation, one targeting the 5 '-UTR (untranslated region; MD3A MO) and the other at the start of the ORF (open reading frame; MD3B MO) of MD3.
